description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for a new challenge? Sussex Community NHS Foundation Trust delivers excellent care at the heart of the community for people living in the coastal area of West Sussex. OneCall Coastal is looking to appoint a motivated and enthusiastic individual to carry out the role of Telephone Referral Coordinator.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;OneCall Coastal is a 24 hour/7 days a week service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is for Thursday and Friday nights, working from 7pm to 7am. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Telephone Referral Coordinator will be based in the OneCall Coastal office in Lancing Business Park, taking referrals for community services and ensuring that all calls and emails are assessed, and that accurate signposting is offered. The post holder will develop the knowledge and capability to refer patients onwards to the appropriate team or service. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Telephone Referral Coordinator will work with a Registered Nurse, ensuring that all calls are referred to the appropriate place and data is recorded. All calls to the service need to be answered within one minute.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer a well-supported working environment and the Trust is committed to supporting opportunities for professional development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Carole Barrow-Team Lead, OneCall Coastal&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;carole.barrow1@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;07787 800774&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Available Monday-Friday, 8am-4pm.&lt;/p&gt;
